     Using Dved - Summary of Commands

CTRL F1  Help

Function Keys

F1  not used		ALT F1	End edit
F2  not used		ALT F2	Quit edit
F3  Open line		ALT F3	Open indent line
F4  Del l (to buffer)	ALT F4	Und l
F5  Reformat line	ALT F5	Reformat paragraph
F6  Select range	ALT F6	Unselect range
F7  Copy from buffer	ALT F7	Clear buffer
F8  Copy to buffer	ALT F8	Append to buffer
F9  Duplicate char	ALT F9	Duplicate line
F10 Duplicate field	ALT F10 Erase field

Cursor Moves

Arrows	  Move cursor	Home	Cursor home
CTRL ->   Next word	Tab	Tab forward
CTRL <-   Back word	^ Tab	Tab backward
^ ->	  End of line	^ Up	Top of screen
^ <-	  Beg of line	^ Down	Bot of screen
Num +	  Next line

Delete operations	Misc operations

Del	  Del c 	ESC	    Enter command
^ Del	  Del c in l	End	    Repeat Command
Backspace Backsp del	Enter	    Enter line
Num -	  Del w 	^ Enter     Indent line
F4	  Del l (buf)	CTRL Enter  Split line
CTRL End  Del Eol

Insert & Copy

Ins	  Insert mode
^ Insert  Insert in line
F3	  Open line
CTRL PgDn Insert page
^ Num +   Copy line
^ Num -   Uncopy line
PgDn	  Copy page
PdUp	  Uncopy page


Command Mode (first strike ESC)

n	       Search for line n
S 'str'        Search for string
S/word	       Search for word
B 'str'        Search back to string
D n	       Del to line n
Dstr	       Del to string
R 'str' 'str2' Replace next str by str2
G 'str' 'str2' Global replace str by str2
